Gameplay

Everyround a team is randomly chosen to be placed above their spawn attempting to kill the other team before they reach the inside of their place. The other team must avoid getting shot on the way there and press the buttons which will kill the other team.

To come in v2

Better prop spawns and more of them. More killing styles (please give suggestions). Better ground and wall design.
